NG0566:1: yang na nyin bzhi'i go rims bzhin //
NG0566:2: drag po'i 'khor lo bskor bar bya //
NG0566:3: che ge mo a mu kam /
NG0566:9: nr-i tsit+ta breng hur thums dza /
NG0566:13: nr-i srog la dun dun rbad /
NG0566:16: khyer phung mugs ti ling shag lo dza /
NG0566:17: srog rtsa khrag ti snying phyung thum ril ram shag rbad /
NG0566:18: gsod pa spu gri'i mtshon cha ste //
NG0566:19: lus srog 'byed pa'i sngags su bstan //
NG0566:20: zla ba tha chung mar ngo la //
NG0566:21: drag po'i las la sbyar bar bya //
NG0566:22: 'khor lo'i mtshon cha me dbal gyis //
NG0566:23: rtsa srog shes pa 'brel bar byed //
NG0566:24: sngags kyi bstod tshigs bar bar du //
NG0566:25: spyi rgyugs sngags kyi phu sprugs bya //
NG0566:26: dgongs kyi ro longs rub dus su //
NG0566:27: drag po kha thun sngags kyis gdab //
NG0566:28: rgyun gyi 'dzab kyis khog phub la //
NG0566:29: gshin rje nag por khram la gdab //
NG0566:30: nyungs kar sngags kyis bla dgug cing *//
NG0566:31: dug khrag thun gyis bsnun cing gsad //
NG0566:33: las kyi sbyor ba rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0566:34: tshes gcig dag tu brtsis pa yi //
NG0566:35: nyi ma sa 'og song ba la //
NG0566:36: dur khrod gnas sam klu yi grong *//
NG0566:37: 'byung bo'i gnas su gnan pa bya //
NG0566:38: gnan pa'i las rnams rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0566:39: zor gyi kha gso rgyun mi gcad //
NG0566:41: dpal gshin rje gshed po ya ma ra dza sku khros pa'i rgyud las //
NG0566:42: kha thun nag po 'khor lo gcod byed kyi le'u
NG0566:43: ste bzhi pa'o // // de nas rdo rje snying
NG0566:44: po yis // kha thus 'khor lo nag po yi //
NG0566:45: las kyi rim pa de lta na //
NG0566:46: 'chi bdag las kyi gshin rje rnams //
NG0566:47: gshed ma srog la rbad pa dang *//
NG0566:48: drag po thun gyis gsad pa yi //
NG0566:49: thun gyi ngan sngags ji lta bu //
NG0566:50: 'jam dpal khros pas nges gsungs pa //
NG0566:51: gdug byed gshin rje pho mo rnams //
NG0566:52: 'di nas byang phyogs ri bo'i rmang *//
NG0566:53: dpag tshad brgyad khri mar 'das na //
NG0566:54: rgya mtsho'i gling gi bar dag na //
NG0566:55: thod pa lcags kyi mun khang na //
NG0566:56: gshin rje yongs kyi sde dpon po //
NG0566:57: ma mo kun gyi tshogs rje bo //
NG0566:58: klu bdud yongs kyi srin po ste //
NG0566:59: gson gshin gnyis kyi zam kha pa //
NG0566:60: gson pho brkos la 'debs par byed //
NG0566:61: shi ba kun gyi gshin bu rje //
NG0566:62: gshin rje nag po dgra bo'i gshed //
NG0566:63: bdud po mi zan skye 'gro'i bdud //
NG0566:64: bye ba gung ring sus mi zlog / me lce klog gi 'phreng ba can //
NG0566:65: lag na be chen 'khor lo thogs //
NG0566:66: zas su dam nyams srog dbugs za //
NG0566:67: ma he nag po zhon nas rgyu //
NG0566:68: thog dang ser ba zhal nas 'bebs //
NG0566:70: khram la thob la ltong la \u0f84rgyus //
NG0566:71: be chen rgyob la 'khor lo skor //
NG0566:72: bdud mo khrag gi ral pa can //
NG0566:75: sha khrag srog dbugs bdag mo ste //
NG0566:76: las kyi rlung dmar zhon nas ni //
NG0566:77: lag na thod pa'i khrag spyo zhing *//
NG0566:78: 'du ba rnam bzhi'i nad gtong ma //
NG0566:80: khram la thob la stong la rgyus //
NG0566:81: khram mda' bu yug char ltar phob //
NG0566:82: sprul pa gshin rje nag po'i tshogs //
NG0566:83: pho brang lcags mkhar glong dgu nas //
NG0566:84: 'chi bdag gshin rje las la rgyu //
NG0566:85: gshin rje chos kyi rgyal po ni //
NG0566:86: mthing nag ma he sngo nag chibs //
NG0566:87: lag na ral gri zhags pa thogs //
NG0566:88: bka' nyan gshin rje phya sangs ni //
NG0566:89: dkar skya zla ba'i 'khor lo zhon //
NG0566:90: lag na tshe srog bum pa thogs //
NG0566:91: mgo 'khor byed pa'i gshin rje dang *//
NG0566:92: tshe srog sdud pa'i gshin rje yis //
NG0566:93: tshangs pa'i rtsa chen gcad pa'i phyir //
NG0566:94: khram la thob la stong la rgyus //
NG0566:95: mtshon chas gtubs la 'khor los skor //
NG0566:96: gshin rje'i rgyal po ya ba ti //
NG0566:97: sngo nag chu glang sngon po zhon //
NG0566:98: lag na ral gri dgra sta thogs //
NG0566:99: bka' nyan gshin rje rtel pa ni //
NG0566:100: nag po rnga mo rlung la zhon //
NG0566:101: lag na gsod byed mda' gzhu bsnams //
NG0566:102: khrag tu skyug pa'i gshin rje dang *//
NG0566:103: srog dbugs len pa'i gshin rje dang *//
NG0566:104: mgrin pa'i rtsa chen gcad pa'i phyir //
NG0566:105: khram la thob la ltong la rgyus //
NG0566:106: mtshon chas chod la 'khor los skor //
NG0566:107: gshin rje a ba glang mgo ni //
NG0566:108: dud kha dre rta rkang gsum zhon //
NG0566:109: lag na lcags kyu zhags pa thogs //
NG0566:110: bka' nyan gshin rje smigs pa ni //
NG0566:111: sngo nag rlung sha rwa bcu zhon /
NG0566:112: lag na ber kha zhags pa thogs //
NG0566:113: rgyal bar byed pa'i gshin rje dang *//
NG0566:114: bla srog len pa'i gshin rje yis //
NG0566:115: lte ba'i rtsa chen gcad pa'i phyir //
NG0566:116: khram la thob la ltong la rgyus //
NG0566:117: mtshon chas gtubs la 'khor los skor //
NG0566:118: gshin rje ral ba tshar dgu ni //
NG0566:119: ljang nag gdug pa sbrul la zhon //
NG0566:120: lag na zhags ba dbyug pa thogs //
NG0566:121: bka' nyan gshin rje mig dmar ni //
NG0566:123: lag na spu gri zhags pa bsnams //
NG0566:124: gsod bar byed pa'i gshin rje dang *//
NG0566:125: srog rtsa gcod pa'i gshin rje yis //
NG0566:126: snying gi rtsa chen gcad pa'i phyir //
NG0566:127: khram la thob la stong la rgyus //
NG0566:128: mtshon chas gtubs la 'khor los skor //
NG0566:129: gshin rje'i khram khram khram la thob //
NG0566:130: gsod byed gshin rje'i chung ma ste //
NG0566:131: nag mo ral ba 'bebs pa mo //
NG0566:132: bdud kyi lcam mo khrag mig ma //
NG0566:133: mon mo gser gyi rna cha can //
NG0566:134: nyams pa'i dgra bo bsgral ba'i phyir //
NG0566:135: khram la thob la ltong la rgyus //
NG0566:136: myos pa khrag gi thun phob cig / gsod pa dug gi thun phob la //
NG0566:137: gsod byed gshin rje'i gnas su khrid //
NG0566:138: mtshon cha'i 'khor lo'i rtsibs la skyon //
NG0566:139: gshin rje'i khram khram khram la thob //
NG0566:140: gdug byed gshin rje pho mo rnams //
NG0566:141: gshed dmar srog la bskul bar bshad //
NG0566:142: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis ngan sngags 'di dag gsungs so //
NG0566:145: ru lu ru lu hu~m phat /
NG0566:146: bam ri li ri li rbad nan /
NG0566:148: che ge mo tshal pa tshal pa nan /
NG0566:149: om snying gshogs snying me kha la mu lo b+h+yo /
NG0566:151: om sa sti ru ru gong tra ra dza nan /
NG0566:152: che ge mo ma ra ya nan /
NG0566:153: om mun ya mugs ti subs /
NG0566:154: che ge mo la cho cho /
NG0566:160: khrag thun khong khrag che ge mo'i khong khrag la thum ril ril b+h+yo /
NG0566:161: myos pa khrag la gsod ba dug / gdug pa'i
NG0566:162: mda' la dri la brdeg / zhal gyi dmod pa
NG0566:163: dug mda' ste // 'khor lo'i kha ni thun gyis gcad //
NG0566:164: dpal gshin rje gshed ya mara dza sku khros pa'i rgyud las /
NG0566:165: gshed dmar srog la bskur zhing thun gyis gsad pa'i
NG0566:166: le'u ste lnga pa'o // // de nas rdo rje
NG0566:167: sny-ing po yis // gdug byed 'chi bdag bskur ba dang *//
NG0566:168: thun gyis gsad pa de ltar na //
NG0566:169: las rnams kun gyis ma grub na //
NG0566:170: gsad pa las kyi thus kha ru //
NG0566:171: 'chi bdag gshin rje spang smad kyi //
NG0566:172: dmod pa'i drag sngags ji ltar bsgrub //
NG0566:173: 'jam dpal khro bos nges gsungs pa //
NG0566:174: 'chi bdag gshin rje nag po yi //
NG0566:175: gsad pa las kyi thus kha ru //
NG0566:176: drag po sbad smad ar la gtad //
NG0566:177: zhal dang 'khor lo'i dmod pa yis //
NG0566:178: ma grub sbogs dang shi sa bstan pa yis //
NG0566:179: gsang ba'i drag sngags bstan pa yin //
NG0566:180: thog mar byang chub sems ldan pas //
NG0566:181: dur khrod dgon pa de dag tu //
NG0566:182: mi bsad g.yul gyi phung sa la //
NG0566:183: man+dal mda' gang gru bzhi la //
NG0566:184: dbus su gru gsum chag gang rtsig / bang rim
NG0566:185: gsum ldan nag po byug / gtor ma bdud rtsi
NG0566:186: rak+ta dang *// gshin rje pho mo'i dam rdzas bsag / mon dang snrel dri'i thod pa la //
NG0566:187: mkhas pas gshags la 'chi bdag bri //
NG0566:188: pho dang mo yi drag sngags ni //
NG0566:189: g.yas dang g.yon du ma nor bri //
NG0566:190: beb sa ti sang ha'i mgo / bskyed la spyan drangs dbang bsdu mchod //
NG0566:191: lto ru a mu rni dza gzhug / tshas ldan dar nag re bas gtum //
NG0566:192: 'brub khung bcug la ro lam brgyad //
NG0566:193: ting 'dzin rnam gsum rim pa las //
NG0566:194: gshin rje gshed po gsal bar bya //
NG0566:195: las kyi gshin rje gsal bar bya //
NG0566:196: bskyed dang spyan drangs mchod pa dbul //
NG0566:197: gshed dmar srog la rbad par bya //
NG0566:198: de nas nyin mtshan dmod par bye //
NG0566:199: dgongs kyi grob so byung ba dang *//
NG0566:200: ro langs las la rub dus su //
NG0566:201: dmod pa sngags kyi phu sprug bya //
NG0566:202: las rdzogs brag dang chu 'thab bam //
NG0566:204: thod sbrul drag po'i las su bshad //
NG0566:205: gzhan yang pho mo'i thod pa'am //
NG0566:206: dur khrod ro ras de dag la //
NG0566:207: mkhas pas 'khor lo bris byas la //
NG0566:208: pho mo gzhan gyi dmod pa dgod //
NG0566:209: nyi ma bzhi ru las sbyar na //
NG0566:210: las rnams grub bar dpa' bos bshad //
NG0566:211: nyin mo gdug pa pho yi sngags //
NG0566:212: ma' ra ya yis dgra bo sgrol //
NG0566:215: ma ra nr-i dza'i sgra las drang *//
NG0566:216: gsang ba sngags kyi spu gri las //
NG0566:217: rno dbal sngags kyi so brdar la //
NG0566:218: dmod pa nyin mtshan bsnol mar drang *//
NG0566:219: spyi rgyugs sngags kyi char phab la //
NG0566:220: bla dgug khram la gdab par bya //
NG0566:221: myos ba'i thun gyis rab snyugs la //
NG0566:222: gdug pa can nam shi sar gtad //
NG0566:223: gzhan yang dmod pa'i las bya na //
NG0566:224: rab chad thod par gru gsum e //
NG0566:225: dug khrag ldan pas bris byas la //
NG0566:226: drag po'i dmod pa dril ba'i mchog / bzlas shing gzugs la trag tu brab //
NG0566:227: las rdzogs lung dang mthun par gnan //
NG0566:228: drag po sngags kyi grangs rdzogs kyang *//
NG0566:229: lus srog mngon du ma phye na //
NG0566:230: sngags kyis yi ge lto nas zlog / dkrugs pa'i sngags kyis shi sa bstan //
NG0566:231: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyi 'chi bdag dmod pa dug gi spu gri 'di dag gsung so //
NG0566:232: ya ma ra dza gshin rje sa to yam //
NG0566:233: ya ma ra gshin rje mug to yam /
NG0566:234: ya ma ra dza gshin rje kha to yam /
NG0566:235: ya ma ra dza gshin rje snying to yam /
NG0566:236: ya ma ra dza gshin rje khrag ti yam /
NG0566:237: ya ma ra dza kha thun dus bsdus /
NG0566:238: ya ma ra dza sum b+h+yo /
NG0566:239: gshin rje nag po dun b+h+yo /
NG0566:240: kring kring ma ra tsa ma ni /
NG0566:242: klad pa go ro tsa na gshogs //
NG0566:243: snying kha rag snying kha rag / rag sha dug
NG0566:244: thun du ru shag / rag sha ma tang ni
NG0566:245: dza b+h+yo / ru lu ru lu /
NG0566:247: ma mo las kyi thun phob /
NG0566:249: dmod pa spu gri'i sngags su bshad /
NG0566:250: om many+dzu shri ya ma dza sa to me ya /
NG0566:251: ya ma snying to me ya /
NG0566:252: ya ma khrag to me ya /
NG0566:253: ya ma mu to me ya /
NG0566:254: nag po ya ma ri dza /
NG0566:256: nag po rag sha dgra bo ma ra ya bam ril rbad ya /
NG0566:258: rag mo nri sha ku ru thums /
NG0566:259: rbad rbad ma ra ya myos myos /
NG0566:260: long long rbad rbad 'dar yed yed /
NG0566:262: dgra bo ma ra dza rbad ya /
NG0566:263: las kyi gshin rje'i dmod pa ste //
NG0566:264: yab yum gsang ba'i dril sngags yin //
NG0566:265: gzhan yang las kyi brgya kha ru //
NG0566:266: 'chi bdag ar la gtad par bya //
NG0566:267: dbyar dgun gnyis kyi tha chung la //
NG0566:268: zhag grangs bcu gnyis gcig tu bsgrub //
NG0566:269: dkyil 'khor mthing nag gru gsum la //
NG0566:270: tha ma thal chen spar khab gtang *//
NG0566:271: thod ngan ro ras ga 'u la //
NG0566:272: drag po sbad smad 'khor lo bri //
NG0566:273: thod pa'i nang du a mu kam //
NG0566:274: thod pa bya rog rjes can du //
NG0566:275: gtor ma bshams la 'chi bdag mchod /
NG0566:277: dkar shal ma dang nyi zla dang *//
NG0566:279: de la 'jigs pa'i sems spangs te //
NG0566:280: 'chi bdag drag sngags bzlas shing brdeg / kram ha ra /
NG0566:283: b+h+yo ru lu ru lu he ya me /
NG0566:285: ya ma ma ra ya snying kha raka tra /
NG0566:287: ya ma ma ma ra ya snying kha rag / raka tra ya su ma ti /
NG0566:289: hu~m tra la ra ya tsa dang */
NG0566:293: ko ta ma ra ya tsit+ta du ha ma dza dza /
NG0566:294: 'chi bdag rgyu ba'i dus su brdeg / rdzogs dang gnan gtad rim par bya //
NG0566:296: ya ma ra dza sku khros pa'i rgyud las /
NG0566:297: drag po spad smad ar la gtad pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o ///
NG0566:298: / de nas rdo rje snying po yis //
NG0566:299: gsang ba'i mthus ka de ltar na //
NG0566:300: bskyod pa zor gyi thus ka gang *//
NG0566:301: 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyis nges gsungs pa //
NG0566:302: bdud kyi lcam mo khrag mig ma //
NG0566:303: srin mo 'jigs byed re ma ti //
NG0566:304: srog thig gsang ba'i thun sgrub brtsam //
NG0566:305: ri gsum rtse 'am chu gling du //
NG0566:306: dug las sprus pa'i man+dal bya //
NG0566:307: mthing nag gru gsum thod 'phreng mdzes //
NG0566:308: rgya gram thod pa gru chad ldan //
NG0566:309: sgo bzhi dur khrod ldan par bya //
NG0566:310: dbus su bse mkhar dar 'phen can //
NG0566:311: bya na bzhi dang tsit+ta brgyan //
NG0566:312: ma mo dre zhon mdung thung 'dzin //
NG0566:313: dur khrod rgyan ldan ral pa can //
NG0566:314: spyi gtsug rgya gram nyi ma can //
NG0566:315: thod 'phreng zhing chen g.yang gzhi dang *//
NG0566:316: re lde sbrul nag khro chung 'bar //
NG0566:317: phyogs bzhir gsod byed srin mo bzhi //
NG0566:318: seng ge stag chen glang dang 'brug / kun kyang snying 'byin thod khrag 'dzin //
NG0566:320: mtshan ngan ban d+har dug khrag bsres //
NG0566:321: nyungs kar nyungs nag ske tshe bstim //
NG0566:322: thod ngan ling kha bcas la brab //
NG0566:323: sngags pa gshin rje gshed bsgoms la //
NG0566:324: thugs kha'i snying po sngags bcas pas //
NG0566:325: gtso bo'i thugs khar bzlas pa 'am //
NG0566:326: bzlas pa'i sngags kyis srog phrogs la //
NG0566:327: 'phrin las bdag mor de mngag go / gtor ma rak+ta bdud rtsis mchod //
NG0566:328: srog snying bzlas shing dam rdzas btab //
NG0566:329: dkyil 'khor dbus su nag mo'i sku //
NG0566:330: khro gnyer 'jigs par bshad pa dang *//
NG0566:331: me yi phung po 'thor ba dang *//
NG0566:332: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khyil dang rlom //
NG0566:333: lci 'thob 'od sgra sgrub khang 'tsheg / 'dod pa mthong nas gsad pa brtsam //
NG0566:334: zhag gsum bdun nam bcu bzhi yis //
NG0566:335: gsad pa drag po'i las rnams brtsam //
NG0566:336: phur gdab zor 'phang mtshon gyis gtub //
NG0566:337: ling ga dur khrod mun gling gnan //
NG0566:339: gsang ba thus ka'i las su bshad //
NG0566:340: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis drag po thun gyis sngags 'di gsungs so //
NG0566:341: om sa ma ya many+dzu shri ya man ta ka
NG0566:342: ya ma ra dza ma ma a ka dza ti
NG0566:343: dza dza / raka mo te kum dza dza kha la ma hi b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0566:344: snying kha raka srog la b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NG0566:347: ma hi srog la dza dza /
NG0566:348: ma mo rak+mo ki li srog la dun dun dza //
NG0566:349: trag rak+sha ma hi srog la breng breng */
NG0566:351: trag sha ma hi dun b+h+yo /
NG0566:352: re ma ti dgra bo'i srog la hur thums thums ma ra ya rbad rbad /
NG0566:353: spyi dang khyad par bsnyen pa ste //
NG0566:354: drag po gsad pa'i las rdzogs pa //
NG0566:355: srog tig yang tigs gsad pa yin //
NG0566:358: mugs bla rtsa la dza dza /
NG0566:359: rtsa bo che la dun mugs /
NG0566:360: nang khrol smad lnga la rtsa bo //
NG0566:361: thun bam thun ri ri li li rbad /
NG0566:362: bla srog 'gugs shing gsod pa ste //
NG0566:364: khram sngags nag mo 'dis kyang gdab //
NG0566:366: ar+ya a rtsa la khram ma dug tsa tsa tshal pa tshal pa rbad rbad /
NG0566:368: che ge mo srog rtsa la mugs ti rbad /
NG0566:370: ma mo khrag la dun ti rdubs //
NG0566:371: srin po rus la chom chom tshol /
NG0566:372: gshin rje'i khram la lhan lhan thob /
NG0566:373: dgra bo khram kha ri li li nri dza rbad /
NG0566:374: phur pa ya man+ta ka'i sku //
NG0566:375: khrag mig ma dang bcas pa bsam //
NG0566:376: nyin mtshan dus drug dag tu 'am //
NG0566:377: dus ni 'brug sgras tshub mas gdab //
NG0566:378: rtsa dang lus srog 'brel bar bshad //
NG0566:379: dpal gshin rje nag po ya ma ra dza sku khros ba'i rgyud las /
NG0566:380: bdud kyi lcam mo sgrub pa'i le'u ste bdun pa'o //    // de nas rdo rje snying po yis //
NG0566:381: bskyod pa'i zor kha de ltar na //
NG0566:382: gnan pa las kyi thus ka ru //
NG0566:383: klu bdud nag po ji ltar sgrub //
NG0566:384: 'jam dpal khro bos nges gsungs pa //
NG0566:385: gnan pa'i las kyi thus kha ni //
NG0566:386: 'chi bdag klu bdud nag po yis //
NG0566:387: nyin bzhi'i 'khor lo rdzogs byas nas //
NG0566:388: gnyis ra gdug pa'i sa phyogs gnan //
NG0566:389: klu gnas grong ngam dur khrod du //
NG0566:390: sngags kyi tshad ma thod pa yi //
NG0566:392: dur khrod ras la sme khrag byug / tsha ba gsum ldan dug chus byugs //
NG0566:394: thig bzhi btab pas le'u tshe dgu //
NG0566:395: bcu gnyis bcu drug mu khyud gsum //
NG0566:396: dbus su sbrul gyi ra bar ldan //
NG0566:397: gshed bzhi'i gnas su thod pa sprul //
NG0566:398: btson khang rus sbal lto ru ming *//
NG0566:399: bcu gnyis rgya gram sbrul dang me //
NG0566:400: bcu drug mtshon cha rgya gram sbrul //
NG0566:401: na ga klu yi sngags kyis bskor //
NG0566:402: gshed bzhi'i gsang sngags tshan bzhi la //
NG0566:403: spu gri gsad gnan nyin mtshan bsnol //
NG0566:404: skabs su thun sngags spyi rgyugs bzlas //
NG0566:405: rdzogs dang mdze can thod pa 'am //
NG0566:406: klu mkhar sbrul nag lto ba ru //
NG0566:407: dmigs pa 'khor lo dril te gzhug / dar nag gtums la rgya yis gdab //
NG0566:408: gnyan ra gdug pa'i sa phyogs ni //
NG0566:409: byang phyogs gdol ba'i gnas su gnan //
NG0566:410: klu sbrul nag po'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NG0566:411: lto yis gzir la rgya yis gcag / klu bdud ya ma'i pho brang gdab //
NG0566:412: steng du ri rab 'khor lo bskyed //
NG0566:413: rdo rje rgya gram 'gros kyis gnan //
NG0566:414: mchog phur bdun gyis sa la gdab //
NG0566:415: lam du zhugs nas rgya gram bcag / zhag bdun bar du slar mi 'gro //
NG0566:416: sku la phyag rgyas bsdigs dang rbad //
NG0566:417: las rnams ma lus 'grub par gsungs //
NG0566:418: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis klu sbrul nag po'i ngan sngags //
NG0566:419: gsang ba'i dug mda' 'di sku gsung thugs rdo rje las 'thon to //
NG0566:421: dgra bo ma ra ya rbad /
NG0566:422: ya ma me ta k+she ma /
NG0566:426: dgra bo rak+ta tsa ra rbad /
NG0566:428: dgra bo ma ra ya rbad /
NG0566:434: dgra bo'i srog la nri sbur rbad /
NG0566:436: ma ga khams thums myags dgra bo'i srog nri sbur rbad /
NG0566:439: dgra bo'i srog la nri sbur rbad /
NG0566:440: nyin mtshan sngags ni ma nor bzlas //
NG0566:441: thun sngags drag pos skabs su brab //
NG0566:442: nag po bam tsi tsi rgyas /
NG0566:445: shan shan srog la shan sbur sod swaha /
NG0566:446: drag sngags sbyor ba rdzogs pa dang *//
NG0566:447: klu la nges par gtad pa na //
NG0566:448: klu sbrul nag pos nges par 'dzin //
NG0566:449: dpal gshin rje nag po ya ma ra dza sku khros pa'i rgyud las /
NG0566:450: klu bdud sbrul nag 'khor lo'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //  // de nas 'jam pa'i dbyangs kyis ni //
NG0566:451: rdo rje can la nges gsungs pa //
NG0566:452: nyon cig rdo rje snying po che //
NG0566:453: rang bzhin rnam dag spros med las //
NG0566:454: bstan pa'i snying po nges pa'i don //
NG0566:455: gsang ba'i bka' rgyud rol par bshad //
NG0566:456: ma nor las kyi thus kha ru //
NG0566:457: thod pa nag po 'chi bdag gis //
NG0566:458: rang rgyud gshin rje bsgrub pa'i lung *//
NG0566:459: 'khor lo gsum dang phyi nang gsum //
NG0566:460: gsang ba'i yang tig brnag pa'i so //
NG0566:461: las rnams kun la nges par 'phags //
NG0566:462: gsad pa'i zor dang gnan pa yi //
NG0566:463: las kyi thus ka gsang ba 'di //
NG0566:464: rdo rje can gyis nges par long *//
NG0566:465: rtsa ba yan lag gnyis yin te //
NG0566:466: sgrub dang spogs pa'i rim par 'dod //
NG0566:467: don dam skye med spros las 'das //
NG0566:468: ngang la rdzogs pa khro bo'i sku //
NG0566:469: 'bar byed khro bo gtum bag can //
NG0566:470: rang rgyud gshin rje sgrub pa'i lugs //
NG0566:471: 'khor lo tun bsdebs bsgral ba'i las //
NG0566:472: gsang ba don gyi snying po 'di //
NG0566:473: bgrod thob phyag rgya rtogs ldan nam //
NG0566:474: dngos grub thob dang bsnyen pa rdzogs //
NG0566:475: don dang ldan pas 'khor lo bskor //
NG0566:476: de ma yin par rang la sdog / dus kyi zla ba tha chung bzhi'i //
NG0566:477: mar ngo dag la bya ba yin //
NG0566:478: yi ge 'bru shag grong khyer nyid //
NG0566:479: srid pa gsum gyi lto na gnas //
NG0566:480: de phyir 'chi bdag rang rgyud kyis //
NG0566:481: 'khor lo rnam pa gsum du bshad //
NG0566:482: thod pa zhal gyi 'khor lo dang *//
NG0566:483: gcod pa nam mkha'i 'khor lo dang *//
NG0566:485: thebs ldog nges pa'i tshad ma dag / nges par bshad pa 'di lta ste //
NG0566:487: de las 'khor lo thebs pa'i rgyu //
NG0566:488: bgrod thob lha gsal bsnyen pa rdzogs //
NG0566:489: ka bzhi tshugs dang gdung bzhi bris //
NG0566:490: gcud phur bzhi ldan gzer bzhi thebs //
NG0566:491: rnal 'byor dkrug pa'i las rnams rdzogs //
NG0566:492: de yis nges par gcod cing thebs //
NG0566:493: de bzhin ldog pa'i rgyu bzhi ni //
NG0566:494: yi ge lhag chad nor ba @#//
NG0566:497: re ga la rten dri mas gros //
NG0566:498: drag po'i 'khor lo ldog ba'i rgyu //
NG0566:499: de bzhin 'byams pa'i rgyu bstan pa //
NG0566:500: sngags la nan chung 'dzab ma rdzogs //
NG0566:501: las mchog nyams dang gtad yar chungs //
NG0566:502: gnyen po ma bskaur ri rab kyi //
NG0566:504: de bzhin 'khor lo 'gor ba dag / yi ge so sor mi mnyam dang *//
NG0566:505: mgo log yi ge nor ba dag / bsgrubs kyang mi 'grub las rnams 'gor //
NG0566:506: de phyir tshad mas gtan la dbab //
NG0566:507: drag chen 'khor lo bskor bya zhing *//
NG0566:508: thun gyi kha gso rgyun du bya //
NG0566:509: yan lag spogs pa chen po ste //
NG0566:510: zhal dang dmog pa'i 'khor lo yis //
NG0566:511: drag po spad kyi mtha' sdud bya //
NG0566:513: de nas yang ni bshad bya ba //
NG0566:514: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i rgyud //
NG0566:515: lus dang yan lag spu gri'i rgyud //
NG0566:516: gsang sngags nges pa'i rno dbal 'di //
NG0566:517: thugs las gsang ba'i lam du phyung *//
NG0566:518: 'di las 'jigs rten dngos grub mchog / gsang ba'i nges don 'di yin pas //
NG0566:519: ma 'ongs dam can sgrub byed na //
NG0566:520: nga ni de la thugs brtse'o //
NG0566:522: 'khor rnams dga' mgu yi rangs te mngon par bstod do //
NG0566:523: dpal gshin rje nag po sku khros pa'i rgyud las //
NG0566:524: gtad cing yi rang ba'i le'u ste dgu pa'o //
NG0566:525: // de nas gshin rje zla gsang nag po las
NG0566:527: ya ma ra dza sku khros pa rdzogs so ///
NG0566:528: / bal yul rgyal po b+ha su d+ha ra dang */
NG0566:529: bod kyi ban chung sangs rgyas bdag 'dra yis //
NG0566:530: bal yul b+ha ra sa ru bsgyur ba'o //
NG0566:531: bod 'bangs yongs la mi brdal bar //
NG0566:532: rtsis byugs chu brag gnyis la gzhag / ces gsungs so //
